                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-8">
                <section class="resume-section">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12">
                            <article class="mb-4 p-4 flex-fill section-card">
                                <header class="my-2">
                                    <h3>
                                        BSc in Computer Science
                                    </h3>
                                    <div class="my-1">
                                        <span><a href="http://www.cse.du.ac.bd/" target="_blank"
                                                rel="noopener noreferrer">University of Dhaka</a></span> &nbsp;
                                        <address>Dhaka, Bangladesh</address><time>Batch of 2018</time>
                                    </div>
                                </header>
                                <p class="my-2">
                                    <strong class="subtext">CGPA</strong>&nbsp;
